Ireland with Simon Reeve

Travel Documentary hosted by Dominic Ozanne, published by BBC in 2015 - English narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/1/11/Ireland-BBC-Ireland-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Simon Reeve sets out on an epic journey around the island of Ireland - a place steeped in history, culture and belief, but with a complex past.

1)  South 
Simon begins his journey in the south of Ireland, paramotoring with an Irish explorer. On the west coast, he does spot of surfing before climbing Croagh Patrick in honour of Ireland's patron saint. This leg of his journey ends in Malin Head, Ireland's most northerly point.

2)  North 
Starting at the spectacular Giant's Causeway in Northern Ireland, Simon travels down the east coast to the great and rapidly changing cities of Belfast and Dublin. He ends his journey in the stunning Wicklow Mountains.
